                      "move_number": 10,
                      "player": "B",
                      "move": "a5!",
                      "commentary": "This is a key move, preparing to establish a knight on b4. Black must react quickly before White has time to consolidate. For example, if Black instead plays 10...b6? 11 Nd5 Nxd5 12 cxd5 Nb4 13 Rc1 Nxa2 14 Rc7 and White maintains his extra pawn with an active position."
